KMeans Algorithm
=====================
As the dimensions of a dataset increase its difficult to plot data and cluster them.

1.Decide n clusters
2.Init Centroids


3.Assign cluster
4.Move centroids

5.Finish(when the centroids aren't moving).
Follow  3,4,5 till the centroinds not moving

How to decide the number of centroids?
Elbow method is used to decide the number of cluster.

